data.description: New Listing! A Beautiful 2-story single-family home. Located in the very desirable gated community of Chapel Cove. The property consists of remodeled bathrooms, tile flooring on downstairs level and Second Floor has Laminated floors. The house is conveniently across the street to the children's playground and community pool. Great spacious backyard for entertaining. Half of Garage has been converted to an additional room that could be utilized as a 4th bedroom or office. This is an amazing and comfortable home for a family. Low HOA that provides internet, basic cable w/ DVR.
